            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "The aim is to get to Mdumbi early to have a surf. In actuality it turns out that leaving quickly is still very hard for me. A coffee, breakfast and one too many long goodbyes later I’m on the road.",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "color": "default"
