      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I got stuck into some podcasts in the car. I finished off the last interview that Sam Harris did with Will Macaskill that was great. It was discussing the moral issue around what weight the future generations and world should be given when making decisions around what is correct to do and support today.",
