    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "We have a lovely chat and I make a quick lunch of “Transkei nachos” which is basically just Salticrax with melted cheese and some vegetable sautéd in curry paste. People are impressed. The surf seems to be on and we take a coffee down there to check. By coffee I obviously mean a oat milk latte because Julian is Julian. ",
            "link": null
          },
