          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Julian and I smoke dirty rollies and catch up on all matters concerning a well rounded human existence while sitting in camp chairs outside his hut - drinking St Francis brewery beers. Dinner is calling and we whip together a decent curry with the few vegetables that I’ve brought down with me. Some white wine accompanies a lovely time. ",
            "link": null
